text: Franz Kneissl (29 July 1921 - 24 May 1994) was an Austrian bobsledder who competed during the 1950s. He competed at the 1952 Winter Olympics in Oslo in the four-man event, but did not finish. ==References== *1952 bobsleigh four- man results *Bobsleigh four-man results: 1948-64. *Franz Kneissl's biography at Munzinger.de Category:Austrian male bobsledders Category:Bobsledders at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:1921 births Category:1994 deaths
title: Franz Kneissl
